Package: BiocReporting
Title: Resources for reporting on Bioconductor project
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
       person(
        "Vincent", "Carey", role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "stvjc@channing.harvard.edu"), 
        person("Marcel", "Ramos", role = "aut"),
       person("Lori", "Shepherd", role="aut"), 
       person("Martin", "Morgan", role="aut")
    )
Description: Tools for reporting to Bioconductor funding agencies. Obtain
    GitHub commits for multiple repositories within a pre-defined period. 
    Pull the employment information for multiple ORCID iDs via the public
    API. Obtain usage change for users and questions on the Bioconductor
    Support site. Summarize download statistics for Bioconductor software
    packages over multiple years.
